155
00:11:42,311 --> 00:11:45,553
Dad, why say it like that? She didn't do anything!

156
00:11:45,553 --> 00:11:48,693
Don't you ever appear in this town again.

157
00:11:48,693 --> 00:11:52,150
If I ever see you again, I'll kill you! Got it!

158
00:11:53,523 --> 00:11:56,253
- Hey, get out of here.
- I think it's better if you go outside.

159
00:11:56,253 --> 00:11:57,973
