187
00:15:03,083 --> 00:15:05,413
It's a secret from Dae Beom.

188
00:15:05,413 --> 00:15:08,203
"A secret"? Why?

189
00:15:08,203 --> 00:15:10,963
He's doing important work in Seoul right now.

190
00:15:12,423 --> 00:15:15,203
Anyway, let's keep it from him a while.

191
00:15:15,203 --> 00:15:17,103
Okay, I will.

192
00:15:17,103 --> 00:15:21,073
I mean, I can only contact him through you, anyway.

193
00:15:24,523 --> 00:15:27,993
