214
00:17:30,201 --> 00:17:31,885
Kim Bom.

215
00:17:31,885 --> 00:17:34,875
Your friend is here. Eat with him.

216
00:17:35,726 --> 00:17:38,306
Please have a bite, Bom.

217
00:17:39,919 --> 00:17:41,919
Don't force her.

218
00:17:43,188 --> 00:17:47,583
