219
00:17:47,583 --> 00:17:51,883
Don't you think your grandma would be brokenhearted if she saw you acting like this?

220
00:17:54,543 --> 00:17:57,263
Do only your feelings matter until she goes to Heaven?

221
00:17:57,993 --> 00:18:00,703
