222
00:18:29,673 --> 00:18:31,113
Here you go.

223
00:18:31,113 --> 00:18:32,093
What's this?

224
00:18:32,093 --> 00:18:35,603
I bought it for Jun. It was in my car the whole time.

225
00:18:37,143 --> 00:18:39,063
Hey, Jo Ji!

226
00:18:39,063 --> 00:18:42,603
The other one is for you. I know you stayed up all night here.

227
00:18:43,443 --> 00:18:45,083
What?

228
00:18:45,083 --> 00:18:48,783
