248
00:20:27,283 --> 00:20:30,073
- Jung Hoon.
- Get the heck out of here!

249
00:20:30,073 --> 00:20:33,463
- Get out of here! Get out!
- Jung Hoon!

250
00:20:35,583 --> 00:20:39,323
