255
00:20:49,213 --> 00:20:52,733
My son, Geun Ho, never did this!

256
00:20:52,733 --> 00:20:56,023
- I can't take this anymore. I'll kill them!
- Please calm down!

257
00:20:56,023 --> 00:20:58,783
Please believe my words!

258
00:20:58,783 --> 00:21:00,363
Please trust what I said.

259
00:21:00,363 --> 00:21:02,623
